Class MethodStructure

java.lang.Object
info.kgeorgiy.ja.chulkov.implementor.MethodStructure
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConstructorStructure
public class MethodStructure extends Object
Structure that parse and keeps information about method to implement it. Generates string for method implementation by toString()
